Pronunciation:
Notes: <b>OED online:</b> Bong n. A kind of water-pipe used for smoking marijuana. Chiefly U.S. <b>wikipedia</b> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bong   Apocryphal history suggests the term "bong" returned to the U.S. with troops who had served in Vietnam, as a corruption of the Thai word baung, which refers to a hollow pipe or tube. <b>Internet search Feb 2006:</b> also used in N Amer, Austral, Canada, Sth Africa, Uk, Ireland.
